style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Strikeforce:_Shamrock_vs._Le\" title=\"Strikeforce: Shamrock vs. Le\">Strikeforce: Shamrock vs. Le</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0.1em; font-weight: bold;\">Strikeforce: Melendez vs. Thomson\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0 0.2em 0.1em\"><a href=\"/wiki/Strikeforce:_Young_Guns_III\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Strikeforce: Young Guns III\">Strikeforce: Young Guns III</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Strikeforce: Melendez vs. Thomson</b></i> was a <a href=\"/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts\" title=\"Mixed martial arts\">mixed martial arts</a> event promoted by <a href=\"/wiki/Strikeforce_(mixed_martial_arts)\" title=\"Strikeforce (mixed martial arts)\">Strikeforce</a>. The event took place at the <a href=\"/wiki/HP_Pavilion_at_San_Jose\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"HP Pavilion at San Jose\">HP Pavilion at San Jose</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/San_Jose,_California\" title=\"San Jose, California\">San Jose</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/California\" title=\"California\">California</a> on Friday, June 27, 2008.<sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>  The main event was a match between lightweights <a href=\"/wiki/Gilbert_Melendez\" title=\"Gilbert Melendez\">Gilbert Melendez</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Josh_Thomson\" title=\"Josh Thomson\">Josh Thomson</a> for the Strikeforce Lightweight title.\n</p>\n<meta property=\"mw:PageProp/toc\" />\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Results\">Results</h2><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Strikeforce:_Melendez_vs._Thomson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Results\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\n\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #ccf; color: #000080; text-align: center;\">Main card\n</th></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Weight class\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Method\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Round\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Time\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\">Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Lightweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Josh_Thomson\" title=\"Josh Thomson\">Josh Thomson</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Gilbert_Melendez\" title=\"Gilbert Melendez\">Gilbert Melendez</a> (c)\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td><sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>a<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Light Heavyweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Bobby_Southworth\" title=\"Bobby Southworth\">Bobby Southworth</a> (c)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Anthony Ruiz\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td><sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>b<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Lightweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Billy_Evangelista\" title=\"Billy Evangelista\">Billy Evangelista</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Nam_Phan\" title=\"Nam Phan\">Nam Phan</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (split)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Middleweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\">Eric Lawson\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Jesse Gillespie\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Submission (rear-naked choke)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">1\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">1:03\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Women's Featherweight\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Miesha_Tate\" title=\"Miesha Tate\">Miesha Tate</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;padding-right:5px\">def.\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"><a href=\"/wiki/Elaina_Maxwell\" title=\"Elaina Maxwell\">Elaina Maxwell</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">Decision (unanimous)\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">5:00\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #ccf; color: #000080; text-align: center;\">Preliminary card\n</th></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-right:5px\"